2B181DAC.Line7.BAB4F: They look to the Cathedral for safety and protection. Even for faith.

5D3AB126.Line1.BAB4F: What would the ancients think of me?

9123A42A.Line5.BAB4F: My people are forgetting the old ways. Growing weaker.

C50C972E.Line9.BAB4F: And yet here I remain in the shadows, watching it all slip away.
